Package: gp3ml
Type: Package
Title: Leakage-Safe Predictive Validation for Gazepoint Research
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
 person(
 given = "Stefanos",
 family = "Balaskas",
 email = "s.balaskas@ac.upatras.gr",
 role = c("aut", "cre"),
 comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2444-9796")
 )
 )
Description: Provides governance and validation infrastructure for predictive workflows using
           Gazepoint-derived research data. The package is designed for explicitly labelled,
           non-sensitive methodological and experimental outcomes. Its planned scope includes role
           validation, feature provenance, leakage auditing, group-aware resampling contracts,
           calibration assessment, and reproducibility reporting. It does not provide person
           identification, health inference, protected-attribute prediction, or direct inference of
           emotion, stress, mental state, cognition, comprehension, personality, deception, or intent.
